QueryText: farmer asked about nursery management in paddy
KccAns:
recommended to go for summer ploughing and apply 5 to 10 T OF FYM , and irrigate the field with 5-10 cm of water and go for puddling . Prepare nursery with 10 m length and 1 m width in the puddled field
seed rate for transplanting is 20-25 kg per acre , before going for sowing in the nursery treat the seeds with carbendism  @ 2.5 g per KG of seeds
